          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孤昨晚一梦真少有"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见一个那鱼儿在那水上走"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "它的冷气搜身孤难消受"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "有孤王我正在那高声喊叫无人救"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孤醒来正在那三更后"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "吉凶二字孤解也解不透"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬光",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "兄王说话没来由，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬光",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "梦寐之事何须挂心头！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬光",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "小弟保兄坐龙楼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬光",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人来看过葡萄酿"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "御弟说话孤心受，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你保孤王押诸侯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "押定了一十一国，各国不敢统貔貅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "天下的举子孤为首"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人来推杯你就换大斗"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "御弟为何面带愁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，御弟为何这等模样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小弟不料足尖疼痛难忍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快前去太医院调治！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄长一人在此，弟放心不下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御弟你来看，孤内穿长猊宝铠，外罩锦袍三层。两旁战将千员，料无妨碍。快"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快调治去罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬光",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "谢过兄王龙恩厚，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬光",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "小弟即来献酒酬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬光",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "管叫鱼儿上了钩！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姬光下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，传进肴人走上！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传进肴人走上！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（专诸上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "三皇五帝夏商周，"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "盖世英雄不到头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "命里无来莫强求。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "要把王僚一笔勾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "命中有来终须有"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "鱼中暗藏剑一口"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "手捧鲜鱼朝上走"
        },
        {
          "character": "四校尉",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！作什么的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "进肴的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四校尉",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有夹带？"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四校尉",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等要搜！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "站立了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这才是官差不自由。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四校尉同搜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四校尉",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无有？闪开了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老天爷助我把名留！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见君不敢强抬头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "手捧鲜鱼朝上走"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "霎时一阵寒风透，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这见鱼儿在当头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姬僚",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "快快拿来孤消受"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "管叫王僚一笔勾！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（专诸刺姬僚，四将同打杀专诸。专诸下。柳展熊上，开打。四将同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "柳展熊 （三笑） 哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
